30:50.500 --> 30:52.154
But, uh, if I was you,

30:52.198 --> 30:53.460
I'd probably get
the roast beef.

30:53.503 --> 30:55.462
<i>[apprehensive music]</i>

30:55.505 --> 30:58.465
Yeah, the roast beef...

30:59.945 --> 31:01.511
Roast beef.

31:01.555 --> 31:04.166
Yeah, roast beef.

31:04.210 --> 31:06.952
Great.
