telling left from right.

31:46.165 --> 31:48.036
We'd make jokes about it.

31:48.080 --> 31:49.820
And he'd mix up words.

31:51.648 --> 31:52.911
You know, I've seen
kids like that.

31:52.954 --> 31:54.129
Stevie, don't discharge him
yet, all right?

31:54.173 --> 31:55.478
- Yeah.
- All right.

32:03.225 --> 32:05.010
Damn, you again, huh?

32:05.053 --> 32:06.707
Since you lost consciousness,

32:06.750 --> 32:08.752
