get out of here.

32:19.763 --> 32:21.417
All right.

32:21.461 --> 32:23.985
All right, let's just
get it over with.

32:24.029 --> 32:26.683
Okay, so without
moving your head,

32:26.727 --> 32:28.033
follow my finger.

32:31.645 --> 32:33.734
Good. All right.

