38:58.379 --> 39:01.991
who had been in their life
for a long, long time,

39:02.035 --> 39:03.689
in a completely
different light.

39:05.778 --> 39:08.171
And it--it kind of
got me thinking,

39:08.215 --> 39:12.785
um, you know, I've been, um,

39:12.828 --> 39:14.482
I've kind of been at sea

39:14.526 --> 39:17.616
since you told me that you

39:17.659 --> 39:19.357
couldn't be
my therapist anymore.

39:19.400 --> 39:21.576
And I thought

39:21.620 --> 39:25.885
that that was because
what I missed was

39:25.928 --> 39:29.628
the work that we did together.

39:29.671 --> 39:32.674
But now what I'm thinking,
is maybe...

39:37.070 --> 39:40.290
Maybe what I really miss
is you.

39:40.334 --> 39:46.732
<i>â™ª</i>

39:50.388 --> 39:51.867
- Hi, honey.
- [chuckles]

39:55.828 --> 39:56.916
Come on in.

40:03.749 --> 40:05.620
- Thanks for seeing me.
- Sure.

40:09.407 --> 40:11.234
It's my own space.

40:13.976 --> 40:15.891
