- [chuckles]

40:20.940 --> 40:22.028
And we're self-governed.

40:22.071 --> 40:24.378
No one tells us what to do.

40:24.422 --> 40:25.945
[chuckles]

40:25.988 --> 40:27.903
Oh, honey,
I wasn't talking about you.

40:27.947 --> 40:30.645
It's okay, Mom.
[laughs]

40:33.039 --> 40:34.257
Would you like some tea?

40:34.301 --> 40:35.911
Yeah, that'd be great.

40:35.955 --> 40:38.871
<i>[soft sentimental music]</i>

40:38.914 --> 40:42.178
<i>â™ª</i>

40:42.222 --> 40:43.876
Listen, Mom...

40:46.226 --> 40:47.836
Are you gonna be okay
with me leaving?

40:51.579 --> 40:54.060
I'll be fine, Stevie.

40:54.103 --> 40:55.278
And...

40:56.932 --> 40:59.500
I'm really going
to make it this time.

40:59.544 --> 41:01.502
I know you are.

41:08.030 --> 41:09.423
I love you.

41:09.467 --> 41:15.864
<i>â™ª</i>

41:19.128 --> 41:22.088
